- I thought of putting it away.

09:07.630 --> 09:11.409
Well, why don't you put it away?
Why don't you take the stuff, put it in...?

09:11.509 --> 09:13.076
Sit down, will you?

09:17.849 --> 09:21.127
Now, do you want to hear
my thinking on this?

09:21.227 --> 09:25.547
If I just let things pile up long enough,
we won't be able to find each other.

09:25.648 --> 09:29.260
And if you can't find me,
you can't have me.

09:29.360 --> 09:30.887
