09:30.987 --> 09:32.725
- HOOPER: That makes sense. Ha, ha.
- Yes.

09:33.239 --> 09:35.392
Sonny...

09:35.492 --> 09:38.310
I'm not asking for miracles.

09:38.411 --> 09:42.481
If you could just get the beer cans,
say, 25 feet from...

09:42.582 --> 09:45.526
Ten feet from the trash can. Ten feet.

09:45.627 --> 09:46.989
HOOPER: Hmm.

09:50.799 --> 09:53.660
It's close enough. I'm yours.

09:53.760 --> 09:55.122
(HOOPER CHUCKLES)

10:00.141 --> 10:03.710
- Is your back okay, really?
- It's fine.

10:03.812 --> 10:07.723
- Did you want to walk on it?
- No, I want you to crawl under it.

10:14.531 --> 10:18.059
TONY: All right, we're ready down here.
Could we clear the area, please?

10:18.159 --> 10:20.977
