- Put your hand right through there.

10:23.540 --> 10:26.358
- TONY: You guys ready on the roof?
- MAN 1: Working on it.

10:26.459 --> 10:28.611
- It's tied off? Okay.
- MAN 2: Tied off.

10:28.711 --> 10:31.114
- I love danger.
- TONY: Okay, we're ready down here.

10:31.214 --> 10:32.781
MAN 3: Okay, don't look down now.

10:32.882 --> 10:35.910
- TONY: Roll the cameras!
- MAN 4: Five, six on all cameras.

10:36.010 --> 10:38.413
