- The realie will take the fall with you.

12:16.486 --> 12:18.929
- Oh, for chrissake.
- ADAM: There's my man.

12:19.030 --> 12:22.016
- Make me look great, Sonny.
- I'll make you look great, Adam.

12:22.116 --> 12:26.146
You can't use a real dog, Tony,
for chrissake. He can't hit an airbag.

12:26.246 --> 12:28.231
